ood & EW Rayner\n|1:37.00\n|-\n|1979\n|Polly Porter\n|RB Weaver\n|P Wright, Winton\n|Mrs P Wright\n|1:34.5\n|-\n|1978\n|Copper Belt\n|JW Walker\n|BF Deacon, Hawera\n|K and Mrs Gray \n|1:35.00\n|-\n|1977\n|[[Grey Way]]\n|[[Bob Skelton (jockey)|RJ (Bob) Skelton]]\n|EP Corby, Washdyke\n|PG South\n|1:35.50\n|-\n|1976\n|Tiptoe\n|CP McNab\n|E Ropiha, Woodville\n|AS Fell \n|1:36.5\n|-\n|1975\n|King's Romance\n|[[Bill Skelton (jockey)|WD (Bill) Skelton]]\n|\n|J McKendrick\n|1:33.00\n|-\n|1974\n|An Illusion\n|BP Thomson\n|\n|JP Norman \n|1:35.50\n|-\n|1973\n|Kaukapakapa\n|[[Bob Skelton (jockey)|RJ Skelton]]\n|\n|GD Cameron \n|1:35.00\n|-\n|1972\n|Egmont Park\n|NG Harris\n|\n|IF McGuire\n|1:39.00\n|-\n|1971\n|Panzer Chief\n|GN McLiesh\n|\n|PD Moran\n|1:35.00\n|-\n|1970\n|Honey Belle\n|DA Peake\n|\n|J Sarten \n|1:34.00\n|-\n|1969\n|Carlsberg\n|HN Ruahihi\n|\n|WL Aitken & WW Tatham \n|1:34.50\n|-\n|1968 dead heat\n|Bywon \n|David Peake \n|\n|GP Broun\n|1:35.50\n|-\n|1968 dead heat\n|Nausori\n|BF Andrews\n|\n|Mrs UE Matthews & EB Reid\n|1:35.5\n|-\n|1967\n|Tara's Pride\n|JF Grylls\n|\n|CW Ansford \n|1:34.25\n|-\n|1966\n|Chantal\n|GL Willets\n|\n|Miss LE Jamieson \n|1:36.00\n|-\n|1965\n|Empyreus\n|RW Taylor\n|\n|HN Phelan \n|1:36.25\n|-\n|1964\n|Gymkhana\n|RW Taylor\n|\n|ED Martin\n|1:36.25\n|-\n|1963\n|Rapido\n|WJ Mudford\n|\n|WB Priscott \n|1:35.50\n|-\n|1962\n|Starborough\n|GP Hulme\n|\n|H Cleland\n|1:36.50\n|}\n\n==See also==\n\n* [[Thoroughbred racing in New Zealand|Recent winners of major Wellington and other New Zealand races]]\n* [[Telegraph Handicap]]\n* [[Captain Cook Stakes]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n* [http://www.nzracing.co.nz/ N.Z. Thoroughbred Racing Inc.]\n* http://www.racenet.com.au\n* http://www.nzracing.co.nz\n* http://www.tab.co.nz\n* http://www.racebase.co.nz\n* ''The Great Decade of New Zealand racing 1970-1980''. Glengarry, Jack. William Collins Publishers Ltd, Wellington, New Zealand.\n* ''New Zealand Thoroughbred Racing Annual 2018 (47th edition)