his first big break came with the film ''Yuvatha''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hummaa.com/music/album/yuvatha/35586 |title=Yuvatha : Telugu Movie - Yuvatha Songs, Yuvatha Mp3 Downloads, Yuvatha Music, Yuvatha Lyrics |publisher=Hummaa.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-06}}</ref> in which he penned all the songs. In his career, the lyrics he penned for the songs in the movies ''Ishq'' and ''Gunde Jari Gallantayyinde'' bought critical acclaim.\n\nKrishna Chaitanya made his directorial debut in the film ''[[Rowdy Fellow]]'' starring [[Nara Rohit]] and [[Vishakha Singh]], which released on 21 November 2014 with positive reviews.\n\n==Personal life==\nKrishna Chaitanya was born 2 May 1983 in Eluru. He received his early education from CRR Public School. He studied engineering at Sriram Engineering college Chennai.\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===As Lyricist===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Year\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Film\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Song(s)\n|-\n|2010|| ''[[Brindavanam (2010 film)|Brindavanam]]''|| ''Yuvakula Manasaina'' \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2011|| ''[[Oh My Friend]]'' || ''Sri chaitanya Jr college''\n''Maa Daddy Pockets''\n|-\n| ''[[Pilla Zamindar]]'' ||''Thalabadi'', ''Chuttu Chuttu'', ''Oopiri'', ''Rangu Rangu'', ''PJ Club Mix''\n|-\n|2012|| [[Ishq (2012 film)|''Ishq'']]|| ''Lachamma'', ''Oh Priya Priya'', ''Chinadana Nekosam''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2013|| ''[[Gunde Jaari Gallanthayyinde]]''||''Gunde Jaari Gallanthayyinde'', ''Thu Hi Rey'', ''Ding Ding Ding'', ''Neeve Neeve''\n|-\n| ''[[Swamy Ra Ra]]'' ||  ''Krishnudi Varasulantha'', ''Adhento , ''Edu Vaadu Evado Ledu'', ''Life Ante'', ''Yo Yo Yo Memu Antha''\n|-\n| ''[[Okkadine]]'' || ''Hey Po''\n|-\n| [[Baadshah (2013 film)|''Baadshah'']] || ''Sairo Sairo''\n|-\n