{"title_page": "Boxing at the 1996 Summer Olympics \u2013 Bantamweight", "text_new": "{{short description|Boxing competitions}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox Olympic event\n|event = Bantamweight boxing\n|games = 1996 Summer\n|image = \n|caption = \n|venue = [[McCamish Pavilion|Alexander Memorial Coliseum]]\n|dates = 20 July \u2013 3 August\n|competitors = 31\n|nations = 31\n|gold = [[Istv\u00e1n Kov\u00e1cs (boxer)|Istv\u00e1n Kov\u00e1cs]]\n|goldNOC = HUN\n|silver = [[Arnaldo Mesa]]\n|silverNOC = CUB\n|bronze = [[Vichairachanon Khadpo]]\n|bronzeNOC = THA\n|bronze2 = [[Raimkul Malakhbekov]]\n|bronzeNOC2 = RUS\n|prev=[[Boxing at the 1992 Summer Olympics \u2013 Bantamweight|1992]]\n|next=[[Boxing at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Bantamweight|2000]]\n}}\n{{BoxingAt1996SummerOlympics}}\nThe '''Bantamweight''' class in the [[boxing at the 1996 Summer Olympics]] competition was the third-lightest class at the [[1996 Summer Olympics]] in [[Atlanta, Georgia]]. The weight class is open for boxers up from 54 [[kilogram]]s. The competition in the [[Alexander Memorial Coliseum]] started on 1996-07-20 and ended on 1996-08-03.<ref name=\"SR\">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1996/BOX/mens-bantamweight.html |title=Boxing at the 1996 Atlanta Summer Games: Men's Bantamweight |work=Sports Reference |accessdate=13 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Medalists==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|-\n|{{OlympicGoldMedalist|[[Istv\u00e1n Kov\u00e1cs (boxer)|Istv\u00e1n Kov\u00e1cs]]|HUN|1996 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicSilverMedalist|[[Arnaldo Mesa]]|CUB|1996 Summer}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"#cc9966\"|'''Bronze'''||{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Vichairachanon Khadpo]]|THA|1996 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Raimkul Malakhbekov]]|RUS|1996 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Results==\n{{32TeamBracket-Compact-NoSeeds-Byes\n | R1 = Round of 32\n | R2 = Round of 16\n | R3 = Quarterfinals\n | R4 = Semifinals\n | R5 = Finals